&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid holidays and flexible, take-it-as-you-need-it paid time off&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A culture built on innovation that values big ideas, no matter where they come from&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
