&lt;li&gt;Implement end-to-end operational workflows for offline and online channels, including direct mail drops and paid social campaign setups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate the onboarding of new marketing partners while nurturing existing relationships to sustain long-term channel performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot platform tracking discrepancies, attribution gaps, and software integrations to maintain high data fidelity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to partner inquiries with urgency while assisting external stakeholders with technical navigation and asset delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize campaign budgets, creative configurations, and copy requests by evaluating AI-driven insights with a critical eye to meet performance targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute collaborative campaigns across Product, GTM, Events, Creative, and Brand teams to ensure hit deadlines and boost process efficiency&lt;/li&

